data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
1. You have 26 starting boxes filled with sums, which vary from 1$ to 1 000 000$.
2. You must choose a starting box as your own (down in the textbox by typing a number between 1 and 26, and after that pressing Choose button.)
3. Clicking on the Boxes(buttons), reveals their content and the sum you just lost.
4. An offer from the banker will occur after every 6, 5, 4 and etc., Boxes opened.
5. On the last banker offer you will have the option to swap you box with the last one left, if you decline his offer.
6. You win what you got from the Banker offer, your starting box or the last swapped box.
7. Have fun playing the game.
